  "original_title": "\u0db4\u0dc5\u0dcf\u0dad\u0dca \u0d9a\u0dd3\u0db4\u0dba\u0d9a\u0da7 \u0d85\u0daf\u0dad\u0dca \u0da7\u0dd2\u0d9a \u0da7\u0dd2\u0d9a \u0dc0\u0dd0\u0dc3\u0dd2",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Showers in several parts of the country today",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Showers or thundershowers will occur at times in the Sabaragamuwa Province and in the Kandy, Nuwara Eliya, Galle and Matara districts today (26), the Met Department said.",
        "A spokesman for the department said that there will be several spells of showers in the Western and North Western provinces as well.",
        "He added that strong winds of up to 50 kmph are expected at times in the western slopes of the central hills, in the northern, north central and northwestern provinces and in the Trincomalee and Hambantota districts.",
        "The Department warns the public to take immediate action to reduce the risk of temporary strong winds and lightning along with thunder showers."
      ],
